name: Dynalene EG-XT
description: Dynalene EG-XT is a high-temperature inhibited ethylene glycol. Dynalene ethylene glycol (EG), also known as monoethylene glycol (MEG) or 1,2-ethanediol, is a naturally colorless, odorless, slightly viscous fluid that is miscible in water. Dynalene ethylene glycol products include both inhibited and uninhibited solutions. Dynalene glycols are blended with specially formulated additive packages depending on your system specifications.
